---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="DD52 Released | Takuya Asano"
  description="DD52 is a piano work from the Cadinene period, shaped around pinene, the first breath inside the forest, and the body remembering before thought."
  ogImage="https://asanotakuya.com/images/DD52.jpg"
  ogUrl="https://asanotakuya.com/news/dd52-released"
  ogType="article"
>
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container header-inner">
      <a href="/" class="site-title">Takuya Asano</a>
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/works">Works</a>
        <a href="/news">News</a>
        <a href="/about">About</a>
        <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="section">
    <div class="container narrow">
      <article class="news-post">
        <a href="/news" class="back-link fade-in">← Back to News</a>

        <header class="news-post-header fade-in">
          <p class="news-date">2026.06.28</p>
          <h1 class="news-post-title">DD52 Released</h1>
        </header>

        <figure class="news-post-image fade-in">
          <img src="/images/DD52.jpg" alt="DD52 artwork" />
        </figure>

        <div class="news-post-content fade-in">
          <p>DD52 is now available on Bandcamp.</p>

          <p>A study of pinene.</p>

          <p>
            The first breath<br />
            inside the forest.
          </p>

          <p>
            Before thought,<br />
            the body remembers.
          </p>

          <p>
            Tension opens<br />
            into clear air.
          </p>

          <p>
            No resolution,<br />
            only the instant of entering.
          </p>

          <p>DD52 is a piece from the Cadinene period, connected to α-pinene.</p>

          <p>
            This work observes the first moment of entering a forest:<br />
            not the memory of a place,<br />
            but the body responding before thought begins.
          </p>

          <p>
            Air enters first as scent,<br />
            then as breath,<br />
            then as a change in the body.
          </p>

          <p>
            Within the Cadinene studies, scent is not treated only as smell.<br />
            It is observed as a physical response,<br />
            a threshold where memory, tension, and clear air briefly meet.
          </p>

          <p>DD52 is the instant before the forest becomes familiar.</p>

          <p>
            <a
              href="https://takuyaasano.bandcamp.com/track/dd52"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
            >
              Listen on Bandcamp
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {
      entries.forEach((entry) => {
        if (entry.isIntersecting) {
          entry.target.classList.add("is-visible");
        }
      });
    }, { threshold: 0.12 });

    document.querySelectorAll(".fade-in").forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
  </script>
  <style>
    .news-post {
      max-width: 720px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .back-link {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .back-link:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    .news-post-header {
      margin-bottom: 32px;
    }

    .news-date {
      margin: 0 0 12px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .news-post-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.12;
      font-weight: 400;
      letter-spacing: 0.01em;
    }

    .news-post-image {
      margin: 0 0 40px;
    }

    .news-post-image img {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 560px;
      height: auto;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .news-post-content {
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .news-post-content p {
      margin: 0 0 20px;
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", "Noto Serif JP", serif;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.72;
      letter-spacing: 0.008em;
      color: #333333;
    }

    .news-post-content a {
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    }

    .news-post-content a:hover {
      opacity: 0.65;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .back-link {
        margin-bottom: 32px;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .news-post-header {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .news-post-image {
        margin-bottom: 28px;
      }

      .news-post-image img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .news-post-content {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .news-post-content p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.68;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
